headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Discounts
content:
Those looking to get in on all that diminutive automotive mayhem can do so by taking 30% off the cost of the Dinka Veto Classic, as well as a range of other vehicles in all shapes and sizes.

- Karin Futo GTX - 30% off
- Dinka Veto Classic - 30% off
- BF Weevil - 40% off
- Kosatka Submarine - 30% off

And more! Check out the Rockstar Newswire for more details.
